      • areJavaClassesCompiled

        protected boolean areJavaClassesCompiled()
        Check if Java classes should be actually compiled by the task. This method is overridden by InstrumentIdeaExtensions task in order to suppress actual compilation of the java sources.
        Returns:
        true if the java classes are compiled, false if just instrumentation is performed.
